data.Name: Space Laces
data.Bio: Ian Slider, also known by his alias, Space Laces, is an American dubstep artist, who utilizes heavy use of sound design in his tracks. He gained popularity in 2013 for his collaborations with Excision & Downlink on the Destroid project, however he was famous before he started Space Laces, due to releasing music on Newgrounds as cornandbeans. Under this alias, Ian uploaded a bunch of house and electro songs from 2006 up until 2013. He gained support from various Newgrounds users, with his music being used in various animations and games.
